---
title: Carb Smart Chicken Thighs Dinner with Creamed Spinach Sauce and Roasted Veggies
description: This flavour-packed chicken dinner is the stuff mealtime dreams are made of. Hearty roasted veggies are served alongside juicy chicken thighs topped with a generous creamed spinach-inspired sauce. It's giving chophouse vibes from the comfort of your own kitchen.

